	<name>Dynamic Wallpaper Editor</name>
	<summary>Create or edit XML dynamic wallpapers ("background slideshows") for the GNOME desktop</summary>
	<description>
		<p>Dynamic Wallpaper Editor is a simple utility to create or edit dynamic wallpapers for the GNOME desktop.</p>
		<p>The duration of each picture and each transition can be set separately or globally.</p>
	</description>
